                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="clearfix"> </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="recent-grid">
                                    <div class="wom">
                                        <a href="#"><img src="~/tema2/images/7.jpg" alt=" " class="img-responsive" /></a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="wom-right">
                                        <h4><a href="#">Integer rutrum ante eu</a></h4>
                                        <p>
                                            Mauris fermentum dictum magna. Sed laoreet aliquam leo.
                                            Ut tellus dolor, dapibus eget.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="clearfix"> </div>
